7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Artbreeder and Canva AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Upscaling, Style Transfer, Commercial License. Where Artbreeder pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Image To Image, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Canva AI uniquely offers Inpainting and Outpainting, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Artbreeder holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while Canva AI scores 7/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Artbreeder and Canva AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Artbreeder's free tier and Canva AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
